The '''Minister of Defense''' was the head of the [[Ministry of Defense (Five Worlds)|Ministry of Defense]] and successor to the position of [[Minister of War]]. The Minister was in charge of civilian matters concerning the [[Corellian Defense Force/Legends|Corellian Defense Force]] and was a member of the [[High Cabinet]]. The first Minister was [[Rorf Willems]].

